ComicInfo.Title: Behold... The Living Planet!; Valhalla!
ComicInfo.Summary:
Behold... The Living Planet!: Thor wins over Ego, the Living Planet and gets Earth's freedom from the colonizers. Jane wanders into the New Men and is offered a job as a teacher in Wundagore.
Valhalla!: Harokin rides the Black Stallion of Doom to Valhalla.
